{"tid":510878,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"摩佬有火：3億鎊唔夠爭霸","createTime":"2017-12-27T02:32:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-27T03:03:29.000Z","uid":333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"52330f0ca8f310503bb87663e62a710f80d1e4bc","tid":510878,"uid":333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T02:32:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=zJ4NV0q7rwvv%2F7cjtf6SgosQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=c62322a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】曼聯周二英超主場失禮地以2:2逼和般尼，領隊摩連奴再同記者劍拔弩張，並揚言即使有3億鎊也不足爭標。<br />\n<br />\n曼聯一度落後0:2，幸而後備入替的連格大顯神威，梅開二度，扳成2:2平手，避免「拆禮物日」送禮。被記者問到上任後已豪擲3億鎊擴軍，紅魔主帥摩連奴（Jos&eacute; Mourinho）忍不住反擊：「還不夠，曼城有力用收購前鋒的價錢羅致後衛（暗指基爾獲加），要知道，班霸買人的價格往往高於其他球隊，」<br />\n<br />\n「班霸同勁旅是兩回事，我深明班霸意味著甚麼。」每當扯火時，摩佬也會滔滔不絕反駁：「難道你們不認為AC米蘭同曼聯不同層次？難道皇馬遜於曼聯？難道國際米蘭不是班霸？歐洲足球有很多班霸，但未必每一季都有力爭標，悠久歷史造就了班霸的地位。」<br />\n<br />\n「當你們說爭標時，曼聯永遠是當仁不讓，難道熱刺不是嗎？難道阿仙奴沒責任爭標？車路士呢？」摩佬補充道。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faa9a2b21b7f50eafab18446780461acaf49b2cf","tid":510878,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T02:36:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf61a0c510f8ddce25d6750ee22993d0816c508b","tid":510878,"uid":39508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T02:38:44.000Z","msg":"摩佬真係技窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢幾年輸俾控球在腳，迫搶，體力化足球輸到傻左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢種踢法明追住你大巴來踢點守都輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bd1074cd25f3525245760c4da45c9